&gt;&gt; Low.

00:08:31.350 --> 00:08:40.150
&gt;&gt; GOLEMAN: Low. Random. It's random. It's
zero, because graduate school entry exams

00:08:40.150 --> 00:08:46.330
are designed to predict one thing only--that
is, how well you'll do your first year in

00:08:46.330 --> 00:08:57.130
graduate school. They do that very well. The
