00:18:07.340 --> 00:18:14.600
hypothalamic-pituitary-adrenal axis. This
is--this creates a rush of stress hormones,

00:18:14.600 --> 00:18:22.810
it changes the entire way the brain prioritizes
information. Once this axis has been triggered,

00:18:22.810 --> 00:18:32.770
it means that, for example, if the emotion
