00:18:32.770 --> 00:18:40.090
us is what preoccupies attention. It captures
attention. It changes the hierarchy within

00:18:40.090 --> 00:18:45.500
the memory so that we remember and think about
only what pertains to the thing that is scaring

00:18:45.500 --> 00:18:52.770
us at the moment. And it does all the other
